---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="Sam Lauder is a Melbourne-based architectural photographer specialising in architecture and the built environment."
>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-layout">
      <div class="about-image">
        <img
          src="/images/about/portrait.jpg"
          alt="Sam Lauder, architectural photographer"
          loading="eager"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="about-content">
        <h1>About</h1>

        <div class="about-body">
          <p>
            I'm a Melbourne-based photographer specialising in architectural and interior photography. I work with architects, interior designers, developers, and builders to document the built environment with clarity, craft, and a considered eye.
          </p>
          <p>
            My approach is collaborative. I take time to understand each project before arriving on site, whether that means reviewing drawings and precedents, visiting at different times of day, or simply having a conversation with the design team about what makes the work distinctive.
          </p>
          <p>
            I've worked across commercial, civic, hospitality, and residential projects with clients including Fieldwork Architects, Woods Bagot, WMK Architecture, Studio Esteta, Hayball, and GroupGSA.
          </p>
          <p>
            Based in Melbourne, available nationally.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-contact">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline">Get in Touch</a>
          <a href="mailto:SamLauderPhotography@gmail.com" class="email-link">SamLauderPhotography@gmail.com</a>
        </div>

        <div class="about-clients">
          <h2>Selected Clients</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Fieldwork Architects</li>
            <li>Woods Bagot</li>
            <li>WMK Architecture</li>
            <li>Studio Esteta</li>
            <li>Hayball</li>
            <li>GroupGSA</li>
            <li>Sibling Architecture</li>
            <li>FJC Studio</li>
            <li>MORC Interiors</li>
            <li>Canva</li>
            <li>Urban Climb</li>
            <li>Metricon</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    padding: 4rem 0;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-image img {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .about-content h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .about-body p {
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .about-body p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .about-contact {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin: 2.5rem 0;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-outline {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.75rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    text-decoration: none;
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--color-text);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-outline:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .email-link {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .email-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .about-clients {
    padding-top: 2.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .about-clients h2 {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .about-clients ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0.5rem 1rem;
  }

  .about-clients li {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
      padding: 3rem 0;
    }

    .about-image img {
      aspect-ratio: 3 / 2;
      max-height: 400px;
    }
  }
</style>
